emuInput.TitMainTitle: LaGene Wilson, Jackie Fletcher, Bunny Lawther, and Ruth Pacella gathered around table with YWCA "Y" Teens display of boats, another version
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 15, 1955, pg. 25, reads: "'All Aboard!' with 'Y-Teens' - 'Y-Teens' throughout the U. S. are celebrating 'Roll Call Week,' Oct. 9-15, as the 'YW' marks its 100th anniversary this year. Theme of this year's 'Roll Call' is 'All Aboard - Go With Us.'  'Y-Teens- expect to exchange scrapbooks with teen-agers of nearly forty other countries.  Peabody High 'Y-Teens' pose with their 'ships' for promoting international understanding.  Left to right: La Gene Wilson, 'Jackie' Fletcher, 'Bunny' Lawther and Ruth Pacella. - Harris Photo."
